 Monorail using Google Pay on Android phones. Google says more cities and transportation services are on the way.<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rFAIysO_H8d011M4TybbtPxvdwg=/1400x0/filters:no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/10454383/google_pay_las_vegas_monorail.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FrFAIysO_H8d011M4TybbtPxvdwg%3D%2F1400x0%2Ffilters%3Ano_upscale%28%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_asset%2Ffile%2F10454383%2Fgoogle_pay_las_vegas_monorail.png&h=4ecf095f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2018/3/19/17138776/google-pay-contactless-transit-tickets-las-vegas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2018%2F3%2F19%2F17138776%2Fgoogle-pay-contactless-transit-tickets-las-vegas&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cda0bd04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2018/3/19/17138776/google-pay-contactless-transit-tickets-las-vegas</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"&quot;In order to use nanaco mobile, a cell phone compatible with Osaifu-Keitai is required. &quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=en&amp;rurl=translate.google.com&amp;sl=ja&amp;sp=nmt4&amp;tl=en&amp;u=http://www.nanaco-net.jp/about/nanacomobile/&amp;xid=17259,1500000,15700021,15700124,15700149,15700168,15700173,15700186,15700201&amp;usg=ALkJrhjCeZBAOmO7VyXznkMpwFCy5qXsXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.googleusercontent.com%2Ftranslate_c%3Fdepth%3D1%26hl%3Den%26rurl%3Dtranslate.google.com%26sl%3Dja%26sp%3Dnmt4%26tl%3Den%26u%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.nanaco-net.jp%2Fabout%2Fnanacomobile%2F%26xid%3D17259%2C1500000%2C15700021%2C15700124%2C15700149%2C15700168%2C15700173%2C15700186%2C15700201%26usg%3DALkJrhjCeZBAOmO7VyXznkMpwFCy5qXsXg&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=740cb203\" data-au